review_blob: Growler from COAST.  Pours red/brown with a good head.  Unfiltered.  Some hop aroma.  Very bitter-hoppiness (word??) with a nice mellow malt finish.  Great Hoppy Red Ale.  Another great beer from COAST!
Out of 12 oz bottle.  Poured clean with very little head. Smell was smokey with a little hint of caramel. Good roasted malt flavor. All in all, not bad for a quick drinking beer
beer_name: Sierra Nevada Tumbler Autumn Brown Ale
